] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.16015-ref13">13</xref>] 以及专家的意见，我们得到表4所示的评估指标的灰类和表5所示的评估指标延拓值与实际值。</p></sec><sec id="s5_6"><title>4.6. 指标隶属度的计算</title><p>对于指标x<sub>11</sub>，根据<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2550096x40_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，可得：</p><p>图2. 样本矩阵A</p><p>图3. 标准化矩阵R</p><table-wrap id="table2" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table2">Table 2</xref></label><caption><title> Weight of the second inde</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"  >经济Y<sub>1</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"  >管理Y<sub>2</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"  >技术Y<sub>3</sub></th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>11</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>12</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>21</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>22</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>31</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>32</sub></td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >权重</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.4674</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.5326</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.4778</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.5222</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.1324</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.1187</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >指标</td><td align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="6"  >技术Y<sub>3</sub></td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>33</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>34</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>35</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>36</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>37</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >X<sub>38</sub></td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle"